messages.message: If you are using MSFT OCR, you have to use the co-ordinate normalization, so likely something the Reader team has to fix.

```def __get_scale_factor(width, height, unit, width_px, height_px):
  if unit == 'inch':
    width = float(width) * 96
    height = float(height) * 96
  
  x_scale = float(width_px) / width
  y_scale = float(height_px) / height

  if unit == 'inch':
    x_scale = x_scale * 96
    y_scale = y_scale * 96

  return x_scale, y_scale```
